title: waffles
description: its probs not the best recipe, but its rly simple
source: somewhere on the internet i forgot
---
§recipe
	§ingredients
		250g flour
		half packet baking powder
		100g butter
		1 pinch of salt
		50g sugar
		3 eggs
		50cl milk
	§/ingredients

	§instructions
		make fountain from the flour sugar bake powder and salt
		put in the whole eggs and mix well
		melt the butter and put it in
		put in milk bit by bit until its smooth
	§/instructions
§/recipe
